quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,62,"Ɓeen goonɗinɓe eɓɓen feewɓe e nasaara en e ɓe ngalaa diine,kala goonɗinɗo Alla e ñalaande wattan o golli ko moƴƴi ɓeen keɓata njoɓdi to Jooma maɓɓe kulol alanaa ɓe te kamɓe ɓe cunotaako"
  2,63,Nde Min ɓami aadi mon Min ummini fello Tuur dow mon ƴettee ko Min ngddani on e semmbe ciftoree ko woni heen mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,64,Fawii heen caggal ɗuum nduŋti-ɗon taw naano ɓural Alla e yurmeende Makko dow mon maa on njeye e bonnoraaɓe
  2,65,On nganndii ɓeen tooñɓe e mon ñande hoore-biir (samdi) Min mbii ɓe ngontee baaɗi booraaɗi
  2,66,Min mbaɗi ɗum woni maande teskuye wonande ɓe e aroyooɓe e tinndinoore wonande hulɓe Alla ɓe
  2,67,"Muusaa wi'i yimɓe makko Alla yamirii on nde kirsoton nagge ɓe mbii mbela nanngir-ɗaa min ko ɗaayɓe? o wi'i: miɗo moolii Alla jeyeede e majjuɓe"
  2,68,"Ɓe mbii du'ano min Jooma maa O laɓɓinana min no nge wa'i. O wii: ko nge wonaa nayeye wonaa ñalel ko hakindiinge mbaɗee ko njamira-ɗon ko"
  2,69,"Ɓe mbii torano min Jooma maa O laɓɓinana min ngoobu (kulor) magge ? O wii: Oon wii ko sooye no feewi enge weli laarde"